ing: 1/2 cup kalamata olives, pitted and sliced
des: "Ground turkey makes a great burger. It makes an even better one with feta cheese and kalamata olives. Serve these tasty treats with sun-ripened tomatoes and Greek-style pita."
ins:
Preheat the grill for medium high heat.
In a large bowl, combine turkey, feta cheese, olives, oregano, and pepper. Mix together, and form into patties.
Lightly oil the grate. Place patties on the grill.  Cook for 10 to 12 minutes, turning halfway through.
